N2  - The article consists of dialogue about research and articles published in ?Academy of Management Review.? Arthur G. Bedeian refers to an article by Barry and Elmes (1997), which discussed strategic management and discursive practices in scientific writing. David Barry and Michael Elmes respond to readers' comments. A study by Roberts and Greenwood (1997) focused on transaction cost economics and institutional theory. Peter W. Roberts and Royston Greenwood respond to comments from Kimberly Bates and refer to a constrained-efficiency framework for analyzing organizational design adoption.
AB  - The article consists of dialogue about research and articles published in ?Academy of Management Review.? Arthur G. Bedeian refers to an article by Barry and Elmes (1997), which discussed strategic management and discursive practices in scientific writing. David Barry and Michael Elmes respond to readers' comments. A study by Roberts and Greenwood (1997) focused on transaction cost economics and institutional theory. Peter W. Roberts and Royston Greenwood respond to comments from Kimberly Bates and refer to a constrained-efficiency framework for analyzing organizational design adoption.
